夜一起想不起我曾被愛<br />\n難道分手會令感動再來<br />\n<br />\n誰叫我這樣活該 縛起雙手給你愛<br />\n愛到兩腳浸沒在大海不懂再走開<br />\n<br />\n熟悉的想講再會 陌生的都很匹配<br />\n難怪我永遠懷念飛灰<br />\n<br />\n嫌棄你想再會 被丟低想反悔<br />\n誰叫我要靠別人待薄才配<br />\n<br />\n熟悉的想講再會 陌生的都很匹配<br />\n難怪我永遠懷念飛灰<br />\n<br />\n如何不後悔"},{"pid":"270e9b6c631e99be99fbd97eebd1dcd55163e9a8","tid":127004,"uid":36163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識野</blockquote><br />\n我要聽歌虐待自己 聽乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a720dba13c7519615eabe230928d92bb5966e047","tid":127004,"uid":36184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:47:51.000Z","msg":"2003年 Third Encounter Concert 黑夜不再來!!! 最撚正version"},{"pid":"5139b8eefa0fb2ae244a64d3e757913b8d033568","tid":127004,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識野</blockquote><br />\n我要聽歌虐待自己 聽乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n浪費"}]}